704433f-a.title: Brooklyn: Franklin Avenue - Myrtle Avenue
704433f-a.text:
(1)
157-173 Franklin Ave.,..east side, between Myrtle Ave., and Willoughby
Street.  Also seen is the Franklin Ave.n Italian Presbyterian Church. at
no. 161-171 Franklin Awe.
July 22, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, an earlier view.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
